Package it.polimi.se2019.adrenalina.event.invocations

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Invocation
    An invocation is a particular type of event used to execute methods on the view of a client when using a socket connection.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ShowBoardInvocation
    Invocation to print the game board on the client.
    ShowBuyableWeaponsInvocation
    Invocation to show a list of buyable weapons on the client.
    ShowDeathInvocation
    Invocation to print the death of a player on the client.
    ShowDirectionSelectInvocation
    Invocation to show the direction selection for a movement on the client.
    ShowEffectSelectionInvocation
    Invocation to show the effect selection for a weapon on the client.
    ShowFinalRanksInvocation
    Invocation to print the final ranks on the client.
    ShowMessageInvocation
    Invocation to print a message with a certain severity on the client.
    ShowPaymentOptionInvocation
    Invocation to print the player's payment options on the client.
    ShowPowerUpSelectionInvocation
    Invocation to show the powerUp selection for (re)spawns on the client.
    ShowReloadWeaponSelectionInvocation
    Invocation to show the weapon selection for reloading on the client.
    ShowSpawnPointTrackSelectionInvocation
    Invocation to show the spawn point track selection on the client in case of overkill in domination mode.
    ShowSquareSelectInvocation
    Invocation to show the square selection for shooting on the client.
    ShowSwapWeaponSelectionInvocation
    Invocation to show the weapon selection for swapping weapons on the client.
    ShowTargetSelectInvocation
    Invocation to show target selection for shooting on the client.
    ShowTurnActionSelectionInvocation
    Invocation to show the turn action selection on the client.
    ShowUnsuspendPromptInvocation
    Invocation to print the unsuspend prompt for suspended players on the client.
    ShowWeaponSelectionInvocation
    Invocation to print the weapon selection on the client.
    SwitchToFinalFrenzyInvocation
    Invocation to switch to final frenzy on the client.
    TimerSetEvent
    Invocation to set a timer on the client.
